<div type="edition" xml:lang="kan-Latn" rendition="class:kannada maturity:undetermined">

<!--<h4>First Piece.</h4>-->

<p>
<lb n="1"/>citrabhānusaṁvatsarada māgha su 15 sō <g type="danda">.</g> meṇasinakeṟeya
<lb n="2"/>vūraḷivinali mādana kaliga sirigaṁgaḷu kādi bidaḍe kētaṁ
<lb n="3" break="no"/>ṇāyakare maneyadhikāri kallaṁṇa kētagavuḍa haṁneraḍu
</p>

<!--<h4>Second Piece.</h4>-->

<p>
<lb n="4"/>hiṭṭubesa<unclear>makaḷu</unclear> yippatuvokkalu <gap reason="lost" quantity="5" unit="character"/> dāyi
<lb n="5"/>dēvana<unclear>ja</unclear>dēvanu mukhyavāgi <gap reason="lost" quantity="5" unit="character"/> da bhūmi ma
<lb n="6" break="no"/>llikā<unclear>r</unclear>junadēvara keya <gap reason="lost" quantity="10" unit="character"/> yali kaṁba nālu
</p>

<!--<h4>Third Piece.</h4>-->

<p>
<lb n="7" break="no"/>vattu yidanu pratipāḷisadavanu kaḷiṁge Āḷi
<lb n="8" break="no"/>pidavanu netarugeyi <g type="ddanda">.</g>
</p>

